To change the Windows OS Type for a image reference deployment, remove the WindowsOSVersion

"windowsOSVersion": {
      "type": "string",
      "defaultValue": "2016-Datacenter",
      "allowedValues": [
        "2008-R2-SP1",
        "2012-Datacenter",
        "2012-R2-Datacenter",
        "2016-Datacenter"
      ],
      
Then under OSDiskProfile replace the image reference with the approriate one such as below:

"imageReference": {
                        "id": "/subscriptions/a6b332e0-bb36-4ce8-b692-fdb6ee0bc272/resourceGroups/redhatperformance_group/providers/Microsoft.Compute/images/redhatperfImage2"
                    }
                },
                
                
                
                
